  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/72910e1dd5252fe8d14b75f3dd2c891a.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to face <strong>28 distinct bosses</strong>, each testing your skills and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge intricate bullet patterns, read their movements, and strike at openings to experience the thrill of victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some bosses randomly select one of three special attacks, so even familiar foes can surprise you in each encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No two fights are ever the same. Mastery requires skill, timing, and persistence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.poster.avif?t=1763695197\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.webm?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.mp4?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/3b45eaebf7067dc56606fd21a4ee9b4a.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 playable robots, each with 5 unique passive skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each robot has 3 main weapons and 11 shared sub-weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 skill trees per weapon</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and choose from offered skill cards to craft <strong>your own unique build</strong>.<br>Each run offers new combinations and strategies, letting you experiment with different playstyles and tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.poster.avif?t=1763695197\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.webm?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/b251e218f5fa38df331771b2da4eadfa.mp4?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/54c5f350e62e2ad5f1f87d17837673dd.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn the tide of battle with your robot’s <strong>signature special abilities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear waves of enemies or survive otherwise impossible attacks by timing your ultimate move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Specials can be enhanced at the stage shop or via skill cards for maximum effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use them wisely—timing is everything. Limited charges recharge through enemy drops or shop visits.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.poster.avif?t=1763695197\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.webm?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/7f5b460a8c0485d38eb938b5695ca2cd.mp4?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/73dacb018acfdc0fc18ca45b64a0b0a3.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to earn currency and items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your robots, enhance stats and passive abilities, and prepare for even tougher bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip or enhance items to unlock new effects and transform your abilities, giving you a competitive edge against the most formidable foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the satisfaction of growth and the thrill of tackling ever-stronger enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.poster.avif?t=1763695197\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.webm?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/832c838d9f5fcdb4a5572a6903f6e6dd.mp4?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/20744ab5401a38ca79e41a1d4c89ab3a.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Guardians Of Restoration” delivers <strong>roguelike action shooting</strong> with intense, skill-based gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face relentless bosses, experiment with infinite weapon builds, and unleash devastating robot specials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is a new experience—<strong>define your strategy, perfect your robot, and conquer every boss.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/72910e1dd5252fe8d14b75f3dd2c891a.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to face <strong>28 distinct bosses</strong>, each testing your skills and reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge intricate bullet patterns, read their movements, and strike at openings to experience the thrill of victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some bosses randomly select one of three special attacks, so even familiar foes can surprise you in each encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No two fights are ever the same. Mastery requires skill, timing, and persistence.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.poster.avif?t=1763695197\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.webm?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/6319c623b53dabceec5554b60f6978a3.mp4?t=1763695197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092280/extras/3b45eaebf7067dc56606fd21a4ee9b4a.avif?t=1763695197\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 playable robots, each with 5 unique passive skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each robot has 3 main weapons and 11 shared sub-weapons</p